dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:14:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b514e6305bd685b49600b84c6800137a3c02ba34","tid":314504,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本食過即劏即切呑拿魚腩真係返唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n琴日朝先係築地食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef0cce8a1c9ba16ff8e264979f71cad988238a9","tid":314504,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本人唔食三文魚</blockquote><br />\n問緊你，你又理撚得人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW謠言當事實嚟講真係唔可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算無見過都算，<br />\n使唔使教你點用Google？<br />\n<br />\n利申：三文魚派"},{"pid":"a49b31fb3ff3ea9e776ea3ec5bad7402ad4dcc7a","tid":314504,"uid":53730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚吞&gt;靚三&gt;平三&gt;平吞</blockquote><br />\n結論<br />\n窮撚：三&gt;吞<br />\n父幹：吞&gt;三"},{"pid":"be5913ad78149c60fe6e734be93082df58311d0b","tid":314504,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靚吞&gt;靚三&gt;平三&gt;平吞</blockquote><br />\n結論<br />\n窮撚：三&gt;吞<br />\n父幹：吞&gt;三</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5015667525e3e7f18b2d7e8ea1844ba78cdf8a9e","tid":314504,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大拖&gt;三文魚白腩&gt;中拖&gt;呑蓉&gt;三文魚腩&gt;三文魚&gt;赤身</blockquote><br />\n中拖最正 大拖太肥</blockquote><br />\n赤身最正，中拖太肥</blockquote><br />\n中拖最正，赤身太瘦</blockquote><br />\n赤身冇味</blockquote><br />\n你老味就赤身冇味<br />\n<br />\n赤身味道複雜，要靠師父處理得好先好食"},{"pid":"e0a13270ebcaab674a3c40fb0f25b8272f75dc20","tid":314504,"uid":32689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大拖&gt;三文魚白腩&gt;中拖&gt;呑蓉&gt;三文魚腩&gt;三文魚&gt;赤身</blockquote><br />\n中拖最正 大拖太肥</blockquote><br />\n赤身最正，中拖太肥</blockquote><br />\n中拖最正，赤身太瘦</blockquote><br />\n赤身冇味</blockquote><br />\n你老味就赤身冇味<br />\n<br />\n赤身味道複雜，要靠師父處理得好先好食</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n咪傻啦，如果赤身本身唔靚你點漬同熟成都唔會有用<br />\n<br />\n正確處理條魚係基本，但係以日式料理手法好難將一樣唔靚既食材化腐朽為神奇，因為日式料理大部份手法都係用最少嘅調味去呈現食材本身嘅味道"},{"pid":"96166825c85d31cbad2f200c4f706051f96cb9f6","tid":314504,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T22:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係日本食過即劏即切呑拿魚腩真係返唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n琴日朝先係築地食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食過日本啲靚魚<br />\n就會明白自己一路食開嘅根本唔算係日本菜<br />\n香港都算好，近日本，魚生種類多又新鮮<br />\n其他好多地方根本冇入口日本靚魚，唯有用三文魚加牛油果加沙律醬扮日本菜"},{"pid":"a3afe1e42d5080ba3a1573eff5907c2db6676a6a","tid":314504,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T22:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大拖&gt;三文魚白腩&gt;中拖&gt;呑蓉&gt;三文魚腩&gt;三文魚&gt;赤身</blockquote><br />\n中拖最正 大拖太肥</blockquote><br />\n赤身最正，中拖太肥</blockquote><br />\n中拖最正，赤身太瘦</blockquote><br />\n赤身冇味</blockquote><br />\n你老味就赤身冇味<br />\n<br />\n赤身味道複雜，要靠師父處理得好先好食</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n咪傻啦，如果赤身本身唔靚你點漬同熟成都唔會有用<br />\n<br />\n正確處理條魚係基本，但係以日式料理手法好難將一樣唔靚既食材化腐朽為神奇，因為日式料理大部份手法都係用最少嘅調味去呈現食材本身嘅味道</blockquote><br />\n咁要比當然係同一條吞拿魚嚟計啦，新鮮切出嚟嘅赤身真係冇咁好食嘅，但係處理過之後佢嘅味道係好細緻又複雜嘅美味"},{"pid":"cd6e6200c5974ed7ded41b9ad2a700bd724d45a1","tid":314504,"uid":18241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T23:55:52.000Z","msg":"真三文魚不吃日本人"},{"pid":"f6e9c9102892b539e879a6af20214534ee59a968","tid":314504,"uid":32689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n中拖最正 大