未食過靚嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n赤身都仲要分靚唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我同免仔巴對於赤身既處理放法有唔同見解<br />\n但我都想問句，未食過靚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正如A5 都唔一定大部分都係脂肪，A5都可以有偏赤身重肉味，只不過比一般見到既熱門部位少姐<br />\n<br />\n唔係所有赤身都係同一個質素，冬天搵間二千蚊樓上既壽司店試下啦"},{"pid":"7a243e08ce72ff06f48fcfba6e51fc5eed560348","tid":314504,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>赤身咁難食都有人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未食過靚嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n赤身都仲要分靚唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我同免仔巴對於赤身既處理放法有唔同見解<br />\n但我都想問句，未食過靚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正如A5 都唔一定大部分都係脂肪，A5都可以有偏赤身重肉味，只不過比一般見到既熱門部位少姐<br />\n<br />\n唔係所有赤身都係同一個質素，冬天搵間二千蚊樓上既壽司店試下啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我意思係,你都唔會主動叫赤身,而唔係赤身冇靚野"},{"pid":"9aa06e9e7c9de61a3f80a558b794507d79a7fc88","tid":314504,"uid":32689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>赤身咁難食都有人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未食過靚嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n赤身都仲要分靚唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我同免仔巴對於赤身既處理放法有唔同見解<br />\n但我都想問句，未食過靚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正如A5 都唔一定大部分都係脂肪，A5都可以有偏赤身重肉味，只不過比一般見到既熱門部位少姐<br />\n<br />\n唔係所有赤身都係同一個質素，冬天搵間二千蚊樓上既壽司店試下啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\