al/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9adf45521389689581ef69606c461bdb7d18bee","tid":314504,"uid":26833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T20:29:20.000Z","msg":"鰻魚通殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1591089ebf51593c8cc4d7a80dd3dc2d346893fd","tid":314504,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T20:34:14.000Z","msg":"Budget一般既食三文魚 燒都係三文魚好食<br />\n但比得多少少食刺身 一定撚tuna<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a050d4a4c42b6bac51f35ee819cfae9ece0bb865","tid":314504,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T20:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本人唔食三文魚</blockquote><br />\n話說我岩岩六月尾去左轉東京 係淺草橋一間食壽司既舖同一個日本大叔傾計 佢話佢地個輩係唔太食三文魚 但而家日本後生個代已經係比較鍾意食三文魚 原因係一般價位既tuna性價比真係太低"},{"pid":"7cfc7e499ad85856665f52a4a298a9ac4e089d47","tid":314504,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T20:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Budget一般既食三文魚 燒都係三文魚好食<br />\n但比得多少少食刺身 一定撚tuna<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n燒魚嚟講 銀鱈魚同鯖魚都好食過三文魚"}]}